:0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T16:31:10.000Z","msg":"講粗口冇咩野<br />\n但見過啲MK唔講粗口真係唔識講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04fe48b8248b5ccc1f5c3a91ff21198a6148d73b","tid":121983,"uid":1274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T17:39:48.000Z","msg":"介意。<br />\n<br />\n但如果在適當時候，適當場合，<br />\n同朋友或者情侶，<br />\n有一兩個單字粗口，喺幾有情趣！"},{"pid":"c38e3eba4c865b07e3386365ec298ae1780130e4","tid":121983,"uid":77643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T06:31:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講粗口冇咩野<br />\n但見過啲MK唔講粗口真係唔識講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n偏偏好多女仔就係中意依類金毛MK仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f4155f97e3871cf28103f26a8636688d9e4f30d","tid":121983,"uid":77643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T06:35:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>介意。<br />\n<br />\n但如果在適當時候，適當場合，<br />\n同朋友或者情侶，<br />\n有一兩個單字粗口，喺幾有情趣！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n識得個男仔friend爛口到不論場合都會講勁多粗口，仲要句句都一定有，成個燥底小巴佬咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c642cf923056890307b29765667a65ae22ae96a5","tid":121983,"uid":85088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T07:14:40.000Z","msg":"唔會 唔會係我面前扮正經仲好<br />\n但係適可而止 唔好句句都係 同埋睇場合<br />\n利申 巴 都會講粗口"},{"pid":"a21fd2485e83c9331b75828dfc2ae6d58c7c2f86","tid":121983,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T07:20:27.000Z","msg":"最憎人講粗口 因為我自己都唔講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}